  "title": "1 year contract Customer Service ($2800)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Functions:</strong></p><p>- Act as the first point of contact for the customers</p><p>- Understanding both internal and external customers, anticipating customer needs and giving high priority to customer satisfaction</p><p>- Provide satisfactory explanations to customers and take remedial action where necessary</p><p>- To alert superior of recurring service failures so that corrective actions may be taken to avoid future problems</p><p>- Ad-hoc duties that related to contact centre project<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>At least Nitec qualification</li><li>1-2 years customer service experience</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Interested candidates please forward resume in MS Word to royhuang@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p><p></p><p>Roy Huang Peijie</p><p>CEI No: R1104471</p><p>EA License No. 99C4599</p><p>RCB No. 199601303W</p><p></p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.<br /></p><p></p>",
